Resources for System Administrators 

We've created a bunch of business processes for auto insurance in Vlocity. 
You can create new quotes from OmniScript flow, Quote Lightning UI, or Policyholder Site. 
The Auto quote process has details of the quote OmniScript and uses a user-friendly workflow to create a quote. 
Policyholders can follow a guided flow to quickly create quotes from Auto insurance.
